<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>You cannot specify the type of the argument in the where function
Here is the function from Zend_Db_Select :</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
    public function where($cond)
    {
        if (func_num_args() &gt; 1) {
            $val = func_get_arg(1);
            $cond = $this-&gt;_adapter-&gt;quoteInto($cond, $val);
        }
</code></pre>

<p>this should be</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
    public function where($cond)
    {
        if (func_num_args() &gt; 1) {
            list($cond, $val, $type) = func_get_args();
            $cond = $this-&gt;_adapter-&gt;quoteInto($cond, $val, $type);
    }
</code></pre>

